{
  "stem": "22883.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So at that time, of course, the German industry were eager to find workers, and they didn't want to-- to-- well, they preferred, of course, somebody who is-- who is volunteering to work for them than-- than-- than-- the-- the other, you know, forced people.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to this office.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and apparently, they-- shortly speaking, they accepted me and Lilian to go to the Kapfenberg, to that-- to this place, to this Steiermark.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was some procedure, and we had to go to a certain location in Warsaw where they were the-- performing the medical examination.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the-- those people had to sleep there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And until the transport was organized, a group-- When did you arrive in Austria?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- it was, I think, a beginning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think, 16-- I don't remember the date.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was in September, 1943.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We came to Vienna-- to Vienna, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in Vienna, we changed the train, and we came to Kapfenberg, Kapfenberg to that city.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And interesting-- in this Kapfenberg, apparently, the recruiting company who was recruiting people to work for this bohlerstahl company were Danish company.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when we came there, that transport, the two Danish young men appeared, and this was the first time I heard the Danish language.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was wondering, that sounds like German, but I could not understand a word of it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The plant, it was Danish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And those Danish-- interesting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had to go to-- to-- to certain places in this Kapfenberg to-- to receive the certain uniforms and this and those.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they had to escort us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Interesting that they were trying to keep a distance between us.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
